      "role": "user",
      "content": "i used to feel like there was so much color in everything. like even the shadows had a depth to them. but lately... it's just gone. i sit in front of a blank canvas and i feel nothing. no spark, no drive, nothing. it's like the part of me that actually lived is just... dead. i'm just a shell moving through the world.",
